Copy the input file to column A beginning in cell 3
In column B, enter this formula and drag it to the bottom:
  =IF(A3="",SUM(A3:INDEX($A3:A$2002,MATCH(TRUE,($A4:A$2002=""),0))),"") 
Use:
  =max(B3:B)
To find the largest.
Use:
  =sum(LARGE(B1:B,1),LARGE(B1:B,2),LARGE(B1:B,3))
To find the sum of the largest 3.
